{"id":232958629,"title":"儲存硬碟選擇","content":"小弟平常會拍很多照片、影片，在思考該怎麼整理、儲存這些資料。\n\n之前有想過在未來要用NAS機器加四個IronWolf6TB硬碟的方案（最理想），只是覺得成本有點高，近期內無法達成。\n\n由於最近容量也快爆的狀況，開始考慮先單買比較便宜的硬碟來用，目前有\n\n1. WD [藍標] 6TB 3.5吋桌上型硬碟\nhttp://i.imgur.com/ebqNUZZ.png\n2. Seagate 那嘶狼【IronWolf】6TB 3.5吋NAS硬碟 \nhttp://i.imgur.com/U5mYgth.png\n3. 【BarraCuda】新梭魚 8TB 3.5吋桌上型硬碟\nhttp://i.imgur.com/j1LQsmd.png\n4. 【BarraCuda】新梭魚 6TB 3.5吋桌上型硬碟\nhttp://i.imgur.com/6vTNK2j.png\n\n沒用過WD所以不清楚成效如何。但以CP來說應該是要選擇「新梭魚 8TB」，可是「新梭魚」這款雖然價格很便宜但似乎沒有安全的硬碟技術來保護，所以擔心我以後資料的安全。\n\n然後同樣6TB下，IronWolf 多了1400但有硬碟技術保護，應該比較安全吧！\n\n況且以後預計買NAS機的話，新梭魚的硬碟可能也不適合當NAS碟，所以是否選擇 IronWolf比較好呢？\n\n請有研究這塊的各位能給小弟一些建議，謝謝！","excerpt":"小弟平常會拍很多照片、影片，在思考該怎麼整理、儲存這些資料。之前有想過在未來要用NAS機器加四個IronWolf6TB硬碟的方案（最理想），只是覺得成本有點高，近期內無法達成。由於最近容量也快爆的狀況","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0e0bc27b-8c69-4149-b229-04e7a865a09d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T22:55:04.259Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T22:58:09.366Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["硬碟","儲存","電腦","大容量"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"3C","forumAlias":"3c","school":"Wassermann","department":"taiwan_shy_boy","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ebqNUZZ.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/U5mYgth.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/j1LQsmd.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/6vTNK2j.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"124ee7ba-23ee-454b-bbbd-5f803991cbfe","url":"https://i.imgur.com/ebqNUZZl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/ebqNUZZl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/ebqNUZZl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T22:55:04.259Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T22:58